listing_company_name: Purple Cow Real Estate - Greater Springfield
description:
This modern home is what you are looking for. Providing 3 generous sized rooms, 2 bathrooms, main with bath-tub, modern kitchen with dishwasher and stainless steel appliances, air-conditioned open plan living and dining & remote garage.

Currently tenanted till 23 January 2023.

Property features:
O 3 Great sized bedrooms all built with ceiling fans
O 2 Modern bathrooms
O Air-conditioned open plan living
O Spacious kitchen with electric stove top and oven, an abundance of cupboards
O Remote control lock up garage
O Undercover outdoor patio

Situated perfectly in Goodna just a 2 minute walk to IGA, fast-food and more. Close to highway access and just a 30 min drive to Brisbane CBD. Everything you need practically at your door step! location doesn't get much better than this.

Call Sunni 0498 015 283 today to book your inspection. Don't let this opportunity pass you by, as this one won't hang around for too long.

*Images are indicative only and are from a property of the same design and are for advertising purposes only
